## Release v9.0.5

- Fixed a but where shots fired before visiting the trader are frozen and later displayed when leaving the trader again
- Fixed a bug where the information whether the player has attack or cargo drones was not saved
- Fixed a bug where drones did not have any weapons when converting from a cargo drone
- Fixed a bug where drone life was shown above the playing field
- Improved the manual

## Files included

- `void-merchants.p8` — PICO-8 standard cart in clear text format
- `void-merchants.p8.png` — PICO-8 cart image
- `void-merchants_linux.zip` — Linux binaries
- `void-merchants_windows.zip` — Windows binaries
- `void-merchants_raspi.zip` — Raspberry Pi binaries
- `void-merchants_osx.zip` — macOS binaries
- `manual.txt` — Manual for this release
- `LICENSE.txt` — Licensing information